  <summary date="2020-12-08T16:47:48Z" status="Passed House">Puerto Rico Recovery Accuracy in Disclosures Act of 2020 or PRRADA

This bill requires professionals employed in debt adjustment cases involving Puerto Rico to file verified statements disclosing their connections with the debtor, creditors, and other interested parties before seeking compensation for their services.</summary>
